mber=1 |pages=43\u201356 |doi=10.1177/1350506813510423|url=http://liu.diva-portal.org/smash/get/diva2:710302/FULLTEXT01 }}\n* {{cite book |first1=Simon |last1=Oja |first2=Brigitte |last2=Mral |authorlink2=Brigitte Mral |title=The Sweden Democrats Came In from the Cold: How the Debate about Allowing the SD into Media Arenas Shifted between 2002 and 2010 |work=Right-Wing Populism in Europe: Politics and Discourse |publisher=Bloomsbury |place=London/New York |year=2013 |isbn=978-1-78093-343-6 |pages=277\u2013292}}\n* {{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zJFaXe6I74MC&dq|title=From tax populism to ethnic nationalism: Radical right-wing populism in Sweden|first=Jens|last=Rydgren|authorlink=Jens Rydgren|year=2006|publisher=Berghahn Books|isbn=978-1-84545-218-6|accessdate=5 March 2016}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category-inline|Sverigedemokraterna}}\n*{{in lang|sv}} {{official|http://www.sverigedemokraterna.se/ }}\n*{{in lang|sv}} [http://jimmieakesson.se/ Jimmie \u00c5kesson's website]\n*{{in lang|sv}} [http://www.sdkuriren.se/ SD-Kuriren]\n*{{in lang|sv}} [http://www.sdu.nu/ Sweden Democratic Youth]\n\n{{Portal bar|Politics|Sweden}}\n{{Sweden Democrats}}\n{{Swedish nationalism and fascism}}\n{{Swedish political parties}}\n{{Alliance of Conservatives and Reformists in Europe}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:1988 establishments in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Anti-immigration politics in Europe]]\n[[Category:Anti-Islam political parties in Europe]]\n[[Category:Criticism of Islam]]\n[[Category:European Conservatives and Reformists member parties]]\n[[Category:Euronat members]]\n[[Category:Eurosceptic parties in Sweden]]\n[[Category:National conservative parties]]\n[[Category:Nationalist parties in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Far-right politics in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Conservative parties in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Political parties established in 1988]]\n[[Category:Right-wing populism in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Right-wing populist parties]]\n[[Category: